Why don‚Äôt we offer more of these paid opportunities to nonprofit leaders and fundraisers? Instead of hiring on Upwork or Fiverr or something like that, I‚Äôm going to do more hiring from inside. Why don‚Äôt we offer more of these paid opportunities to nonprofit leaders and fundraisers? Instead of hiring on Upwork or Fiverr or something like that, I‚Äôm going to do more hiring from inside.
